{"id": 2741, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心 x 360】你觉得哪些科技产品有助于解决“小型家庭冲突”？", "description": "家里孤老抱怨没人照料、辅导孩子恐惧症，拯救家庭关系，最好来一只哆啦A梦。", "record_count": 11955, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201901152348122Ga5zOWvLskHCX1U.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-16T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 323072, "content": "我觉得要是有台印钞机，什么问题都不是问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 5101, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 323073, "content": "给我妈买了个扫地机器人，她神奇地不催婚了，成天在家调教扫地机", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 323074, "content": "本人北漂，父母年纪大了，现在每天用智能摄像机实时看到家里情况，语音沟通多了矛盾少了", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 323075, "content": "我老公一个985的硕士，死在一堆小学题目上...还好现在有AI智能手表，辅导孩子真的心累", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 323077, "content": "买过360扫地机器人，除了偶尔会偷吸猫粮、充当猫座骑外，扫得还是挺尽心的～", "image": null, "praise_count": 930, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124700}, {"id": 323078, "content": "360安全路由吧，游戏刷剧双开不卡，告别抢网速之战", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433785}, {"id": 323079, "content": "辅导作业绝对是心梗级家庭问题，AI问答功能的儿童手表可以一试", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433920}, {"id": 323080, "content": "之前看到有网友说，人其实跟扫地机器人差不多，都是通过反复碰触南墙，慢慢认识自我的边界。只要撞不坏、不断电，房子迟早能被扫干净的…处理家庭关系也需要有扫地机精神。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1732, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434023}, {"id": 323081, "content": "给家里买过扫地机，我爸经常疯狂和它对话，“你咋不把这张纸吸进去呢？你看你又被卡住哈哈哈！你撞到我音箱了！”……扫不扫得干净是一回事儿，逗老人开心，扫地机比我强…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1975, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433913}, {"id": 323082, "content": "摄像头… 每天隔空监视我家二哈，以防它拆家", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434015}, {"id": 323083, "content": "每次出门忘带钥匙都想抽自己，买了指纹门锁后，算是消除了和自己的矛盾吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434004}, {"id": 323084, "content": "因为扫地问题经常和男票爆发小型争吵，有了扫地机器人后，问题变成了“谁去把它从桌子底下救出来”…… 矛盾也算是，缓和了一些…？", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433986}, {"id": 323085, "content": "扫地机！！妈妈再也不强迫我扫地了！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434028}, {"id": 323086, "content": "买个能限制账号最高网速的路由器，相信我，熊孩子能自动放弃打游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433789}, {"id": 323087, "content": "自从有了360智能门锁，我和我男朋友再也没埋怨过对方“你怎么又没带钥匙”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434056}, {"id": 323088, "content": "自从儿子沉迷于和他的AI手表对话，我的脑子轻松了好多", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433788}, {"id": 323089, "content": "洗碗机", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143922}, {"id": 323090, "content": "360有款智能门铃，防出轨利器，只能帮你们到这了…🙂", "image": null, "praise_count": 989, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733477}, {"id": 323091, "content": "喜欢熊本熊机械键盘", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1559684}, {"id": 323092, "content": "只想要一个情绪检测机！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113807}, {"id": 323094, "content": "扫地机就挺好的，看它们撞墙我还挺开心？？？？【×", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1559603}, {"id": 323095, "content": "最好有个机器人，承包家里所有的家务，当然你要小心，不要变成下一个HER/HIM", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433785}, {"id": 323096, "content": "想要自动剥虾机、剥瓜子机、剥小龙虾机…", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838043}, {"id": 323352, "content": "洗碗机，扫地机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1560605}, {"id": 323097, "content": "说装摄像头的，真的不怕拍到点别的什么嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433843}, {"id": 323098, "content": "印钞机那个！！不要走！\n喂？妖妖灵吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378846}, {"id": 323099, "content": "洗碗机！厨房垃圾处理机！电动窗帘！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1559705}, {"id": 323100, "content": "洗衣机，烘衣机，洗碗机，够了", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540498}, {"id": 323101, "content": "小时候一直被家长管着少看电视少玩电脑，现在爸妈玩手机比我还上瘾，新的路由器上那个控制上网时长的功能真的很管用啊！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 99, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1559701}, {"id": 323102, "content": "可能是人脸识别之类的吧因为不用再输密码了。不过据说化妆前和化妆后差别太大会识别不出来🌚", "image": null, "praise_count": 114, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1550574}, {"id": 323103, "content": "甲方的水军把评论区染得好无聊哦，什么时候有智能去粉（红）机就好了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218083}, {"id": 323107, "content": "带孩子保姆？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433882}, {"id": 323109, "content": "给瘫痪在床的奶奶买了，IPAD。这样她就不会无聊了，还有小爱音箱和家庭摄像头。没孩子还不知道。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512099}, {"id": 323110, "content": "智能爸爸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433929}, {"id": 323111, "content": "陪玩家教", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433996}, {"id": 323112, "content": "写作业神器", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433847}, {"id": 323113, "content": "做饭机？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433995}, {"id": 323114, "content": "一个随叫随到的...我编不下去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433983}, {"id": 323115, "content": "把我老公变成机器人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433900}, {"id": 323116, "content": "智能铲屎官", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433932}, {"id": 323117, "content": "看了一圈留言，你们太恐怖了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433805}, {"id": 323118, "content": "把我自己变成机器人算了!这样我也就不会有任何情绪了", "image": null, "praise_count": 158, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434017}, {"id": 323119, "content": "情绪分析仪", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433962}, {"id": 323120, "content": "有一个机器，让我知道当下我应该说什么才能避免冲突", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433818}, {"id": 323121, "content": "洗衣机 洗碗机 晾衣机 烘干机 扫地机 我就是缺一个保姆", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433911}, {"id": 323122, "content": "那我家里比较和谐，没什么矛盾", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433849}, {"id": 323123, "content": "婆媳关系冲突解决仪？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434042}, {"id": 323124, "content": "印钞机哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434042}, {"id": 323125, "content": "我说什么都能给我发明出来么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433844}, {"id": 323126, "content": "测谎分析仪", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433998}]}